## Summary

| Component | License | Why |
|-----------|---------|-----|
| Code (`src/`) | MIT | Maximum freedom for developers |
| BOK (`bok/`) | CC BY-SA 4.0 | Improvements must be shared back |
| Docs (`docs/`) | CC BY-SA 4.0 | Knowledge should be free and improved |
| Constitution | CC BY-ND 4.0 | Core principles must stay intact |

